# Road Accident Data Analysis (Excel)

## Project Overview
This project analyzes road accident data using Microsoft Excel to identify patterns and trends in accident frequency, severity, and contributing factors.

## Objectives
- Analyze accident trends by time (year, month, day of week)
- Study impact of weather and light conditions
- Identify high-risk road types and locations
- Evaluate accident severity and casualties
- Understand relationship between speed limits and accidents

## Dataset Features
- Accident Index
- Accident Date
- Month, Day of Week, Year
- Junction Control & Detail
- Accident Severity
- Weather Conditions
- Road Surface Conditions
- Road Type
- Speed Limit
- Number of Casualties
- Vehicle Type
- Urban or Rural Area
- Location 

## Tools Used
- Microsoft Excel
- Pivot Tables
- Charts & Dashboarding
- Data Cleaning & Formatting
  


